# nara-design-studio settings — copy this file to `settings.local.md` (gitignored).
# Points the studio at a DS pack. Without it, the bundled neutral starter pack (T1) is used.

- packPath: /absolute/path/to/your/design-system/pack
- outDir: ./design-studio-out
- notes: settings.local.md is never committed and never printed by the skill.
